title: Conor McGregor & Eddie Alvarez Have One Last Intense Stardow at the  UFC 205 Weigh-in's
description: Conor McGregor & Eddie Alvarez have one last tense stare down at the UFC 205 weigh-in's ahead of the main event fight at UFC 205.
